<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="M" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Mercenary1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Mercenary,</orth> adj. venal, hired: <cit><quote>my mind was never yet more m.</quote> <bibl n="shak. mv 4.1.418" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. IV, 1, 418</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>soaked in m. blood,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.7.79" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 7, 79</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>as if I had been m.</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 5.6.41" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. V, 6, 41</bibl></cit>.
